OL,3,CQuick-thinking lifeguards save 13-year-
OL,4,Cold stuck in riptide
OL,6,FHe was helped by colleagues Terri
OL,7,FWarner and Rosalie Longman, who
OL,8,Frescued the boy's uncle who had also
OL,9,Fbeen caught in the tide, and both were
OL,10,Ftaken to hospital.
OL,12,FGeorge said the boy was "pretty worse
OL,13,Ffor wear".
OL,15,F"If we hadn't been alerted to it, the
OL,16,Fsituation could have been a lot
OL,17,Fworse," he said.
