OL,3,CQuick-thinking lifeguards save 13-year-
OL,4,Cold stuck in riptide
OL,6,FRosalie added: "We are advising at the
OL,7,Fmoment due to really strong currents
OL,8,Fthat you stay within your depth where
OL,9,Fyou can touch the floor, so if you do
OL,10,Fget caught in a rip you can bring
OL,11,Fyourself back."
OL,13,FAnton Page, lifeguard supervisor for
OL,14,FPerranporth, said "Our lifeguards did
OL,15,Fa fantastic job in responding after
OL,16,Fhours to two casualties who had been
OL,17,Fcaught in a dangerous rip current at
OL,18,FPerranporth beach.
