OL,3,CQuick-thinking lifeguards save 13-year-
OL,4,Cold stuck in riptide
OL,6,F"Thankfully our lifeguards were still
OL,7,Fon the beach and able to assist but we
OL,8,Fremind people that lifeguards patrol
OL,9,Fbeaches from 10 am to six pm and if
OL,10,Fyou are planning on going in the
OL,11,Fwater, go to a lifeguarded beach
OL,12,Fbetween these hours.
OL,14,F"Furthermore, if you do get in to
OL,15,Ftrouble remember to 'Float to Live' -
OL,16,Flie on your back with your ears
OL,17,Fsubmerged and fight your instinct to
OL,18,Fpanic and wait for help to arrive."
